### Contract Entity Extraction API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api

### 1. Health Check - Root endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Upload Sample Contract (using curl - more reliable for file uploads)
# curl -X POST "{{apiUrl}}/contracts/upload" \
#   -H "accept: application/json" \
#   -H "Content-Type: multipart/form-data" \
#   -F "file=@sample_contract.pdf"

### 2b. Upload Sample Contract (REST Client format)
POST {{apiUrl}}/contracts/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample_contract.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample_contract.pdf
--boundary123--

###

### 3. List All Contracts
GET {{apiUrl}}/contracts
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get Specific Contract by ID
# Replace {contract_id} with actual ID from upload response
@contractId = ddfd9548-dd10-4e22-8c23-bd7163020830
GET {{apiUrl}}/contracts/{{contractId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Get Analytics
GET {{apiUrl}}/analytics
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Delete Contract by ID
# Replace {contract_id} with actual ID
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/contracts/{{contractId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. API Documentation (OpenAPI/Swagger)
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs

###

### 8. API Documentation (ReDoc)
GET {{baseUrl}}/redoc

###

### 9. OpenAPI JSON Schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### CURL COMMANDS (Copy to terminal)
### ============================================

### Upload contract using curl
# curl -X POST "http://localhost:8000/api/contracts/upload" \
#   -H "accept: application/json" \
#   -H "Content-Type: multipart/form-data" \
#   -F "file=@sample_contract.pdf"

### List all contracts
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:8000/api/contracts" \
#   -H "accept: application/json"

### Get specific contract (replace CONTRACT_ID)
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:8000/api/contracts/CONTRACT_ID" \
#   -H "accept: application/json"

### Get analytics
# curl -X GET "http://localhost:8000/api/analytics" \
#   -H "accept: application/json"

### Delete contract (replace CONTRACT_ID)
# curl -X DELETE "http://localhost:8000/api/contracts/CONTRACT_ID" \
#   -H "accept: application/json"

###
